cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the maximum transmit power to an excessively high value of 100 dBm will exceed regulatory limits and cause power control failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將最大發射功率設定為過高的值 100 dBm，將超過法規限制，並導致功率控制失敗。
